                                        <h2 class="page-title">So You Have Received Christ as Lord, Now What?</h2>	
                                        <hr class="page-title" />
					<p class="center" style="text-align: right"><img align="middle" alt="Lost and Trying to Find the Right Way to Go" class="center" height="200" src="assets/images/lost.JPG" title="Lost and Trying to Find the Right Way to Go" width="251" /> </p><p>Having received Christ as your personal Lord and Savior there are a few things you should do next.  The first and easiest step to take is to pray.  Prayer is your one-to-one communication with God.  Through your prayer you can ask God for guidance as you begin to read the Bible.  You can also ask him to lead you to a local church where you can continue to be encouraged by like-minded believers and begin to grow spiritually.  Finally, you can become a witness to what God has done for you.  Please take the time to read more about each of these steps as you begin your journey with Christ. </p><p>If you would like to receive further information feel free to <a href="[~18~]">contact us</a> and someone will help encourage you as you take the next steps.</p>   
